    "For instance, P11 pointed that a character taking a \"quick dip in the well\" did not make logical sense, as wells contain drinking water and are typically too deep to bathe in.",
    "Another example of such an error appeared in a story set in Trivandrum, Kerala, which stated, \"Maya went to the local temple, where she met the priest, Father Thomas.",
    "\"This was logically inconsistent, as a priest named Father Thomas would be associated with a church, not a temple.",
